data.description: Traditional custom built brick home sits on acre &half in Edenton Lake & Harbor community with pool, tennis, clubhouse, beach on the lake.  Enjoy the open spacious floor plan with four bedrooms with en-suite baths. Kitchen has a large island, bar,  lots of cabinets, breakfast nook, with beautiful views of your private back yard. A LEVEL 2 EV CHARGING STATION IN GARAGE. Outstanding floor plan that has many extras.  Great room, family room, dining room, large office area, additional newly finished bonus room/movie room, exercise area, large screen porch. Lots of updates include light fixtures, carpet, gutters, faucets, new refrigerator, dishwasher, tankless hot water heater, & landscaping.  Enjoy swimming, kayak, in the 50 acre lake. Only three miles from downtown Edenton.  Move in ready , immaculate condition.  A Must See!!
